flowchart TD
    A[User opens token sheet] --> B[Choose buy or sell]
    B --> C[Fetch live quote]
    C --> D[Display route, slippage, output, warnings]
    D --> E{Confirm trade?}
    E -->|No| A
    E -->|Yes| F[Prepare transaction]
    F --> G[Sign with active wallet]
    G --> H[Broadcast]
    H --> I[Confirm]
    I --> J[Record execution]
    J --> K[Show result]

